snippet.title: Little Racers Trailer DBP09 - Xbox Indie Games
snippet.description:
So, you think arcade racing games couldn't get any faster? Think again!

Second trailer for Little Racers, an arcade racing game made by Milkstone Studios for Xbox Live Indie Games. Also an entry for Dream Build Play' 09

Currently version 1.3 is available.

The game features online multiplayer, good-looking skidmarks, lots of different cars, each one with its own behavior, many tracks, championship mode, ghost laps, AI racers, and much more.
